  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Regional Coordination of Sahel 2010 Food Crisis, West Africa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">West Africa is responding to a food crisis in Niger, Mali and Chad where food security and nutritional situation is alarming. This is a result of significantly low and poorly distributed rainfall recorded in 2009, resulted in severe lack of pasture and water, as well as a poor harvest.    To be able to coordinate and support the response in those countries, the RC is recruiting for a humanitarian programme officer, a regional human resources advisor, an advocacy advisor and a funding coordinator.    These positions will be funded out of a catfund grant for a period of six months.</narrative>
  </description>
